00:39:32,100 --> 00:39:35,700
Sliction says, stop blaming the model size or the optimizer.

721
00:39:36,240 --> 00:39:40,740
Blame the unrepresentative training distributions that induce these projection collapses.

722
00:39:41,120 --> 00:39:46,580
The model is succeeding perfectly at learning from flawed data that collapses the exact distinctions

723
00:39:46,580 --> 00:39:47,680
the task requires.

724
00:39:47,920 --> 00:39:54,660
And the paper lists these incredibly sharp predictions for other AI flaws that are happening right now,

725
00:39:54,740 --> 00:39:57,840
which require this exact same morphological repair.

